size 係5<br />\nmean 係 (0 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4) / 5 = 2<br />\n咁SST就係 (0 - 2) ^ 2 + (1 - 2) ^ 2 + (2 - 2) ^ 2 + (3 - 2) ^ 2 + (4 - 2) ^２<br />\n因為全部都會square, 所以上邊全部都係&gt;= 0, eg (0 - 2) ^ 2 = +4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以你可以sample 多D, 就會加多d, 新加嘅數一定係&gt;=0, <br />\n咁即係話你加大個sample size,  SST only 會升, 唔會跌"},{"pid":"7f6f1e9e7ddcb31c40e39f07c479ad7c1a1f1c4f","tid":2237391,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69edb3cc88dcaa232fba4afa3ae596e10fba0de","tid":2237391,"uid":304269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"讀緊econometric 見到呢張slide , 唔太明，想問有冇有心人可以深入淺出咁解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"你明顯係大一果時科統計未讀好😂<br />\n之後一學apply econ就見收皮"},{"pid":"3775de88274c8c4c1928bc7fe8e4bbd8e36f8c24","tid":2237391,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Derive variance of slope estimator ，然後再讀次段嘢。呢個係 problem of micronumerosity"},{"pid":"e4515490a0e4292d3dd9893b73c90c07bef4a485","tid":2237391,"uid":304269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6a065351ba28282ab82750f1af5738ae53e7a0","tid":2237391,"uid":73572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔留tg啦<br />\n你知唔知variance 係點計先<br />\ns^2 係sample variance<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3S71hT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3S71hT5.png&h=e222c4a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上邊條式可以寫做<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMTDj75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMTDj75.p